Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a7\fs50\fad(600,600)}Touched by your voice\N你轻声触碰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a7\fs50\fad(600,600)}in the moonlight\N在月光下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.13,0:24:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a7\fs50\fad(600,600)}"Nothing lasts," you said,\N你曾说过：万物不能长久
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a7\fs50\fad(600,600)}But everything still holds meaning in my heart\N但一切铭于我心已是永恒
