Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.99,0:25:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a7\fs50\fad(600,600)}shining smiles...\N明亮的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.48,0:25:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a7\fs50\fad(600,600)}like know flakes, all melted and gone away\N像是飘散的雪花 渐渐融化消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.45,0:25:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a7\fs50\fad(600,600)}Only answer was to live,\N只能这样活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.37,0:25:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a7\fs50\fad(600,600)}and I am still here with your memories\N我仍然在这 紧拥与你的回忆
